      <p>I Love these scones.  You can&#8217;t imagine my disappointment when I went to the fair in Washington and ordered a scone and got some silly dry cake.  I just use Rhodes Rolls to make these, set them out for a few hours, stretch them then deep fry them.  So yummy with honey butter!</p>

